This study dives deep into DNS mainly exploring its root servers, records, and its domain protection strategies. In this paper you can see the different challenges a domain name has to face nowadays there are many small to mid-sized organizations with unique brand names as well as domains but it’s very tough to protect these names. The challenges they have to face is enormous. Some of the problems are Domain phishing, intellectual property (IP) infringement and various other digital attacks. Due to these problems the Organizations are having trouble like loss of trust with customers, and loss of money etc. it’s not easy to solve these problems. But there are some ways to solve these problems and they are some methodologies which can be used to protect against these problems and the use of some digital tools. By using these methods and these tools we can securely safeguard our brands reputation as well as gaining more trust
